text: The 1946 Rhode Island gubernatorial election was held on November 5, 1946. Incumbent Democrat John Pastore defeated Republican nominee John G. Murphy with 54.27% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== *John Pastore, Democratic *John G. Murphy, Republican ===Results=== ==References== 1946 Rhode Island Gubernatorial Category:November 1946 events
title: 1946 Rhode Island gubernatorial election
